Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Serverless computing allows developers to focus on writing code.\n\nThe cloud provider handles all infrastructure management tasks such as server provisioning, scaling, and maintenance.\n\nThis model is ideal for event-driven applications and microservices."
